-- Spain's Colonial says bid for Realia unit worth 650 mln euros
-- By Tracy Rucinski
-- Fri Jul 25, 2014 04:46AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, July 25 (Reuters) - Spanish property company Colonial <COL.MC> said on Friday it has presented a 650 million euro ($874 million) non-binding offer for the Realia Patrimonio unit of debt-burdened real estate peer Realia <RLIA.MC>.

